---
title: North Indian Beef Bowl with Turmeric Rice & Tomato Salsa
description: We're bringing two flavour powerhouses to your place tonight – Mumbai-style spices and turmeric. These spices just so happen to have the magical touch, creating a dinner that's so tasty you'll hardly believe you made it yourself – and in no time too!
